msgid "Otherworldly Visitors"
msgstr "天外来客"

msgid ""
"The yeti howls angrily and draws an image in the snow.  You recognize it at "
"once.  The Visitors.  Mister Yeti clearly wants them eliminated."
msgstr ""
"雪人愤怒地嚎叫着，在雪地上画出一幅图案。你立刻认出来了——访客。雪人显然希望他们被消灭。"

msgid "The yeti growls inquisitively at your progress."
msgstr "雪人发出好奇的低吼，似乎在询问你的进展。"

msgid "Tell the Yeti you have slain the visitors."
msgstr "告诉雪人，你已经击败了访客。"

msgid ""
"The yeti howls joyfully at your triumph over the visitors.  He rummages "
"through his treasure stash and presents you with a metal contraption.  "
"Surely there is some use for it."
msgstr ""
"雪人因你战胜访客而欢呼雀跃。他翻遍自己的宝藏堆，递给你一个金属装置。看起来应该能派上用场。"

