msgid ""
"A big smile passes over the yeti's face as you tell him of your battle with "
"the visitors, but it appears he is not satisfied, yet."
msgstr ""
"当你向雪人讲述与访客的战斗时，他脸上露出灿烂的笑容，但看起来似乎仍然不太满意。"

